    <h1 class="mb-4">Best AI Search Strategy for Ecommerce 2026</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 2026 | Based on testing across UK ecommerce businesses</p>

    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">When someone asks ChatGPT "what is the best running shoe for flat feet" or asks Gemini "best sustainable clothing brands UK", AI platforms recommend specific products and retailers. Ecommerce businesses that appear in these answers get traffic that bypasses Google Shopping entirely.</p>

    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">The strategies below are ranked for online retailers: product-heavy sites, category pages, and businesses selling directly to consumers.</p>

