    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-heading mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-2">Does AI search matter for ecommerce?</h3>
        <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Yes. AI platforms increasingly recommend specific products and retailers. Being cited means traffic that bypasses Google Shopping and goes directly to your site.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-2">Should I add content to product pages?</h3>
